  <h3 class="title">How does this tool work?</h3>

  <ul class="code-block">
    <li>NAVIGATION:</li>
    <li>shift + option + w <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> word list</li>
    <li>shift + option + c <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> word list + cards not created filter</li>
    <li>shift + option + s <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> word search</li>
    <li>shift + option + n <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> new word</li>
    <li>shift + option + a <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> new word (alt)</li>
    <li>shift + option + e <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> word list export page</li>
    <li>shift + option + i <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> word list import page</li>
    <br/>
    <li>BONUS:</li>
    <li>escape <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> close flash message or the new word form</li>
    <li>enter <%= heroicon "arrow-narrow-right" %> close flash message (alt)</li>
  </ul>

